****************************
A customize tools for build your own centos6.x iso.  
Thanks for ljvsss#gmail.com.
****************************

###how to use:
#### 0. environment
>[root@os-builder ~]# cat /etc/redhat-release 

    CentOS release 6.5 (Final)
>[root@os-builder cdrom]# uname -a

    Linux os-builder.fx-dev.net 2.6.32-431.el6.x86_64 #1 SMP Fri Nov 22 03:15:09 UTC 2013 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
#### 1. prepare
# yum -y install anaconda-runtime createrepo yum-utils anacondaanaconda-help busybox-anaconda mkisofs
